$$
\begin{aligned}
& =12\left|\frac{1}{2} \sin \alpha \cos \alpha-\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2} \cos ^{2} \alpha\right|=6\left|\sin 2 \alpha \cdot \frac{1}{2}-\cos 2 \alpha \cdot \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}-\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\right| \\
